{"tid":516020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"八成南亞裔學生申請學生資助遇困難","createTime":"2018-01-01T03:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T10:52:39.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ab115f274bfef1e7779d3826b397957f2314d1e6","tid":516020,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:18:13.000Z","msg":"天主教香港教區勞工牧民中心在今年9月至10月，訪問112位15歲以上南亞裔人士，發現八成受訪者表示申請學生資助時遇到困難，包括不諳讀寫中英文、申請程序太繁複，及不能與學生資助處職員溝通等。調查又發現，65%受訪者獲派英文版「學生資助綜合申請」單張，只有5.3%獲派少數族裔語言的申請單張。<br />\n中心建議，政府應與學校合作，舉辦填表支援服務，支援少數族裔家長填寫申請表及跟進申請。"},{"pid":"347039b6ab19a8d7d924b12065334d0bbca19833","tid":516020,"uid":51978,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:19:36.000Z","msg":"中英文都唔識唔好生存啦 去死啦"},{"pid":"7e3d29ef3b9d11921353d9a081065fd4d94c5f16","tid":516020,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:20:45.000Z","msg":"英文都有困難？"},{"pid":"b4019afb1ce26cfc4207893ff524d2739f813a5a","tid":516020,"uid":106523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:21:39.000Z","msg":"申請八達通咁撚簡單都做唔到<br />\n佢地可以做到d咩"},{"pid":"d8213cbab5d38a825e5a8ade9121b3305f779e92","tid":516020,"uid":1067,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:22:07.000Z","msg":"唔識中文，又唔識英文，咁你就死番去啦"},{"pid":"53c2a152bdefec20cddd21d7d3b8f9771163a5f2","tid":516020,"uid":8867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:22:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e10844739bbf56b9a516a14251fd8f53935f2ec","tid":516020,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:24:09.000Z","msg":"死返去南亞<br />\n賤種"},{"pid":"921b3edfd2162de48ab805e5b17d0eb4007b759f","tid":516020,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b4019afb1ce26cfc4207893ff524d2739f813a5a","tid":516020,"uid":106523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:21:39.000Z","msg":"申請八達通咁撚簡單都做唔到<br />\n佢地可以做到d咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-